summary: This is a search and seizure warrant authorizing the search of Little Saint James Island in the U.S. Virgin Islands on July 24, 2019. The warrant commands law enforcement to search for and seize evidence related to violations of federal law, including property and items described in the attached affidavit.

events.title: Search of Little Saint James Island
events.description: A search and seizure warrant is issued authorizing law enforcement to search Little Saint James Island for evidence related to federal law violations.

locations: Little Saint James Island, U.S. Virgin Islands
keyFacts: A search warrant was issued for Little Saint James Island on July 24, 2019.
The warrant authorized a search during daytime hours (6:00 a.m. to 10:00 p.m.).
The search aimed to seize evidence related to violations of federal law.
The document references an attached affidavit containing facts justifying the warrant.
